0more%20complex%20scenarios%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20I%20believe%2C%20at%20least%20my%20personal%20view%20on%20it%2C%20is%20where%20you'll%20see%20things%20shift%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einstead%20of%20doing%20just%20basic%20annotation%20and%20labeling%20of%20data%2C%20it'll%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20root-causing%20and%20fine-tuning%20that%20data%20to%20help%20the%20AVs%20operate%20and%20navigate%20those%20specific%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20Zoubi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStone%20sees%20a%20similar%20projection%20%E2%80%94%20one%20in%20which%20AI%20models%20improve%20and%20rely%20on%20fewer%20humans%20over%20time%20as%20robotaxis%20get%20better%20at%20adapting%20to%20new%20cities%20and%20their%20quirks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20need%20for%20humans%20will%20trend%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20will%20trend%20to%20zero.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxi-human-labor-industry-data-labelers-annotators-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769939041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697eb334a645d11881886872%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxi-human-labor-industry-data-labelers-annotators-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20human%20annotators%20sift%20through%20data%2C%20labeling%20and%20providing%20more%20context%20around%20the%20driving%20data%20robotaxis%20will%20be%20trained%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxi-human-labor-industry-data-labelers-annotators-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22She%20makes%20six%20figures%20as%20an%20artist.%20It's%20still