ronto%2C%20says%20that%20Canada%20is%20doing%20better%20than%20was%20feared%20a%20year%20ago.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20concerns%20about%20dramatic%20levels%20of%20protectionism%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20all%20but%20complete%20collapses%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20realized%20tariffs%20have%20not%20been%20as%20dramatic%20as%20they%20might%20have%20been%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20The%20effective%20tariff%20rate%20on%20Canadian%20goods%20coming%20into%20the%20US%20is%20still%20under%2010%25.%20Carney%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%20relationship%20with%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20Morrow%20says%2C%20and%20as%20much%20as%20economic%20nightmare%20scenarios%20haven't%20come%20to%20pass%2C%20the%20geopolitical%20outlook%20is%20worse%20than%20expected%2C%20given%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-would-happen-us-leaves-nato-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstability%20of%20the%20NATO%20alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20deterioration%20of%20the%20global%20rules-based%20system%20that's%20been%20in%20place%20since%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20economists%20and%20business%20people%20I%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20agreed%20that%20Canada%20coming%20into%20its%20own%20was%20a%20long%20time%20in%20the%20making.%20From%20Bush's%20%26quot%3Byou're%20with%20us%20or%20against%20us%26quot%3B%20mentality%20post-9%2F11%20to%20Obama's%20%26quot%3BBuy%20America%26quot%3B%20push%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-inflation-reduction-act-means-finances-tax-health-climate-democrats-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBiden's%20industrial%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20America%20has%20been%20acting%20like%20a%20less%20friendly%20friend%20for%20a%20while.%20Trump%20has%20taken%20it%20to%20an%20extreme%2C%20often%20failing%20to%20differentiate%20between%20international%20friend%20and%20foe