%20become%20older%20and%20then%20hope%20to%20make%20all%20these%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20you%20understand%20your%20heart%20health%2C%20the%20better%20equipped%20you%20are%20to%20make%20healthy%20decisions%20for%20future%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232316553-1a6f-42ab-b09a-ef6fc8af12b6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20heart%20may%20be%20aging%20too%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20most%20of%20us%20are%20behind%20in%20our%20investments%20to%20our%20cardiovascular%20health.%20The%20average%20American's%20heart%20is%204%20to%207%20years%20older%20than%20their%20calendar%20age%2C%20according%20to%20Khan's%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20us%20are%20naturally%20driven%20to%20procrastinate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20try%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20things%20that%20are%20immediately%20in%20front%20of%20you%2C%20and%20it's%20harder%20to%20prioritize%20and%20give%20as%20much%20attention%20to%20something%20that%20is%20a%20long-term%20consequence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20online%20tool%2C%20developed%20by%20Khan%20and%20her%20team%2C%20helps%20forecast%20a%20person's%20risk%20of%20heart%20attack%20or%20stroke%20over%20the%20next%2030%20years%20by%20illustrating%20how%20they%20stack%20up%20to%20their%20peers.%20It%20shows%20their%20percentile%20rank%20for%20heart%20health%3A%20in%20other%20words%2C%20out%20of%20100%20people%20the%20same%20age%20and%20sex%2C%20how%20many%20have%20a%20higher%20or%20lower%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhan%20said%20the%20new%20tool%20uniquely%20uses%20percentiles%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20their%20health%20by%20understanding%20their%20risk%20and%20making%20changes%20if%20needed.%20Patients%20can%20then%20prioritize%20which%20habits%20provide%20the%20best%20bang%20for%20their%20buck%20in%20terms%20of%20health%20benefits%2C%20starting%20with%20what%20Khan%20recommends%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22