m%20the%20region.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20also%20attracted%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20wildlife%20%E2%80%94%20from%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20to%20an%20abundance%20of%20bird%20species%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20now%20regular%20visitors%20to%20the%20biosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20saplings%20are%20now%20about%20six%20feet%20high%2C%20and%20when%20you%20walk%2C%20you%20feel%20like%20you%E2%80%99re%20walking%20on%20a%20carpet.%20We%20have%20two%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20who%20visit%20regularly.%20Earlier%2C%20when%20they%20would%20come%20down%20the%20corridor%2C%20they%20would%20stop%20and%20show%20signs%20of%20being%20upset.%20Now%2C%20they%20look%20at%20me%20as%20a%20part%20of%20their%20habitat.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20vision%20of%20coexistence%20is%20coming%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20biosphere%20reserve%20operates%20under%20strict%20rules%3A%20vehicles%20and%20plastic%20are%20not%20allowed.%20The%20only%20exception%20is%20a%20single%20electric%20farm%20utility%20vehicle%2C%20which%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20silent%20safari%20vehicle%2C%20ensuring%20minimal%20disturbance%20to%20the%20animals.%20Visitors%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20bring%20any%20plants%20or%20seeds%20into%20the%20biosphere.%20Every%20effort%20is%20made%20to%20avoid%20activities%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rule%20in%20this%20biosphere%20is%20that%20nature%20comes%20first%2C%20not%20humans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20small%20homes%20on%20the%20property%20for%20overnight%20stays%2C%20built%20without%20cement%20and%20bricks%2C%20using%20prefabricated%20construction%20methods.%20Jai%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20eco-tourism%20s