%3C%2Fem%3E(grow%20aloe%20vera%20and%20earn%20in%20lakhs)%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20farmer%20Hrushikesh%20Jayasing%20Dhane%20(44).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluenced%20by%20this%2C%20several%20farmers%20bought%20thousands%20of%20plants%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F301751%2Fbusiness-school-grad-leaves-london-to-organic-farm-help-farmers-earn-jaivik-jeevan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20them%20on%20their%20barren%20lands%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimagining%20themselves%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20advertisement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20crop%2C%20but%20I%20also%20had%20doubts%20about%20it.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20the%20office%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20market.%20I%20asked%20to%20be%20told%20about%2010%20such%20farmers%20who%20earned%20lakhs%20from%20aloe%20vera.%20The%20local%20officials%20got%20angry%20and%20threw%20me%20out%20of%20the%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20harvesting%20period%20came%20in%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20the%20businessman%20had%20run%20away.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20a%20fraud.%20I%20saw%20farmers%20crying.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20strategy%20to%20market%20the%20crop%2C%20so%20they%20started%20clearing%20their%20fields%20and%20some%20threw%20them%20on%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Interestingly%2C%20Hrushikesh%20picked%20the%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20and%20planted%20them%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20took%20him%20on%20a%20path%20which%20led%20him%20to%20establishing%2C%20what%20is%20today%2C%20a%20multi-crore%20company!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20his%20field.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20village%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20a%20humble%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Hrushikesh%20owned%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Padali%20village.%20The%20family%20had%20traditionally%20been%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20pearl%20millet%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20wheat.%20Despite%20toiling%20hard%20on%20the%20field%2C%20they%20would%20not%20get%20sufficient%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20irrigation%2C%20as%20the%20nearest%20river%20was%20four%20kilometres%20away%2C%20and%20we%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20for%20lift%20irrigation.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20crops%20often%20dried%20up.%20Despite%20having%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20land%2C%20it%20remained%20barren%20for%20much%20of%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20four%20was%20dependent%20on%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20lived